tagger.autotagger
Interface AutoTagger

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public interface AutoTagger
extends java.io.Serializable

This interface represents an automatic tagger, returning tags for a given file. It should also be able to return a description of the algorithm used to return those tags.

Author:
Or Shwartz
